<plot>Leon's co-worker Charlie wants to sell him some sweepstakes tickets. Leon is reluctant, because both his wife and his boss strongly disapprove of gambling. Charlie talks Leon into buying one ticket by offering to put Charlie's name on Leon's ticket. But when the results of the sweepstakes come out, Leon soon finds himself in a complicated predicament.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?066612</url></doc>
